data.description: This well-maintained house has tons of space, offering 2 living areas, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, plus an office space and a loft! Sip your morning coffee on the front porch or play with the kids and dog in your spacious backyard. And did we mention the laundry room is upstairs?? There is lots of room to both work AND play at home! With a new microwave and kitchen island you'll love the heart of this home. It's a must see!!!
